dfischer.utils

Class ChangeNumberOfSimulatedUsersClusterInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.utils.ChangeNumberOfSimulatedUsersClusterInfo

  • public class ChangeNumberOfSimulatedUsersClusterInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Real-time information about the number of users that will be incremented or decremented in future, during a running cluster job. Contains also a small extract of the performance data.
    Since:
    V5.5-D
